  <brief_title>Pediatric Caudal Dexmedetomidine Enhances Postoperative Analgesia of Magnesium Sulphate in Lower Abdominal Surgeries</brief_title>
  <acronym>JASayed</acronym>
  <official_title>Pediatric Caudal Epidural Dexmedetomidine Enhances Postoperative Analgesia of Magnesium Sulphate and Quality of Caudal Anesthesia in Lower Abdominal Surgeries</official_title>
