  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will conduct to compare the efficacy of Magnesium sulphate &amp; dexmedetomidine used
      as adjuvants to bupivacaine in caudal block to provide intra-operative anesthesia as well as
      post -operative analgesia in pediatric patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
